Compute individual squared cosines

Source: R/pca.R
pca_ind_cos2.Rd

Return indivdual squared cosines for each principal component

Usage

pca_ind_cos2(ind_coords)

Arguments

ind_coords

individual coordinates

Examples

library(FactoMineR2)

X_active <- iris[, -5] |>
  standardize_norm()

vectors <- X_active |>
  eigvectors()

X_active |>
  pca_ind_coords(vectors) |>
  pca_ind_cos2()
